content: Hope I'm in the right place...when I click on the zoom link for 11:00 phone bank, it brings me to the zoom page and the dialog with "open link." but when i click that, it goes nowhere. I made sure to open zoom and sign in on  my account and tried again, but the same thing. any suggestions?

hmm... trying to click around on my end and figure this out... if anything, I would try shutting down zoom completely and restarting it (+login) before clicking the link again.

Or it could be that the link is broken (I've done that by accident on the other end of phonebanks, oops.)
trying to get more knowledgeable troubleshooting for you, as well! hope you can connect!
no luck yet...I may try checking my computer for updates, restarting, etc.  I know the zoom app updated a day or two ago
ahh, maybe that's it then. I know my computer goes glitchy for a day or two after it tries to run program updates.
Thankfully, there are plenty more phonebanks for you to join, anytime!
Hi, Peggy -- Are you having any luck getting on your zoom link yet?
Yes-thanks.  Restarted everything, then I was able to connect
great.  I logged on to the call and found a Peggy.  Hoped it was you!  Happy Calling!
